\c 15
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mweya waMwari\x + Num.. 24.2.\x* wakauya pamusoro paAzariya mwanakomana waOdhedhi\x + 15.8.\x*.
\v 2 Iye ndokubuda kunosangana naAsa, ndokuti kwaari: Nditeererei, Asa naJudha wose naBhenjamini. Jehovha anemwi kana muchinaye; uye kana muchimutsvaka achawanikwa nemwi\x + 15.4,15. 34.3. 1 Makor. 28.9. Jer. 29.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*; asi kana mukamusiya, achakusiyai\x + 12.5. 24.20. Det. 31.17. 1 Madz. 18.18. Ezi. 8.22.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino mazuva mazhinji Israeri waiva asina Mwari wechokwadi\x + Hos. 3.4.\x*, uye asina mupristi anodzidzisa, uye asina murairo\x + 17.8,9. 35.3. Rev. 10.11.\x*.
\v 4 Asi pakumanikidzwa kwake wakatendeukira kuna Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri, ndokumutsvaka, iye ndokuwanikwa navo\x + Det. 4.29.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino panguva idzodzo kwaiva kusina rugare kune waibuda kana kune waipinda, nokuti matambudziko makuru aiva pamusoro pevagari vese vedzinyika\x + Vato. 5.6.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino vakagurwa-gurwa, rudzi nerudzi, uye guta neguta, nokuti Mwari wakavatambudza nenhamo dzose.
\v 7 Naizvozvo imwi simbai\x + Josh. 1.6,7,9.\x*, uye maoko enyu ngaarege kushaiwa simba\x + 2 Sam. 17.2. Ezi. 4.4.\x*; nokuti kune mubairo pabasa renyu\x + Gen.. 15.1. Map. 62.12.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Zvino Asa paakanzwa mashoko awa, nechiporofita chaOdhedhi muporofita, wakashinga\x + 15.8.\x*, ndokubvisa zvinyangadzo kubva panyika yose yaJudha naBhenjamini\x + 1 Madz. 15.12.\x*, uye kubva pamaguta aaiva atora kubva pagomo raEfuremu\x + 17.2. 19.4. 13.19.\x*; ndokuvandudza aritari yaJehovha yaiva pamberi peberere raJehovha\x + 8.12.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino wakaunganidza Judha naBhenjamini wose nevatorwa vaiva navo vachibva kwaEfuremu naManase, nevaibva kwaSimioni; nokuti vakamuwira kubva kwaIsraeri vakawanda pavakaona kuti Jehovha Mwari wake anaye\x + 11.16. 16.1.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino vakaungana paJerusarema mumwedzi wetatu, negore regumi nemashanu rekutonga kwaAsa\x + Det. 16.9. Eki. 12.18.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino wakabaira Jehovha nezuva iroro pane zvakapambiwa \add zva\add*vaiva vauya nazvo: Nzombe mazana manomwe, nemakwai zvuru zvinomwe\x + 14.13,15.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino vakapinda pasungano kutsvaka Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba avo nemoyo wavo wose uye nemweya wavo wese\x + 29.10. 34.31. 2 Madz. 23.3. Neh. 10.29.\x*.
\v 13 Uye ani nani asingatsvaki Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri achaurawa, kubva kumudiki kusvika kumukuru, kubva kumurume kusvika kumukadzi\x + Det. 13.9.\x*.
\v 14 Zvino vakapika kuna Jehovha nenzwi guru, uye nekupururudza, uye nehwamanda uye nenyanga dzemakondohwe\x + 1 Makor. 15.28. Map. 98.6. Hos. 5.8.\x*.
\v 15 VaJudha vese ndokufara nemhiko; nokuti vaiva vapika nemoyo wavo wese, nekumutsvaka nechishuvo chavo chose\x + 15.4,15. 34.3. 1 Makor. 28.9. Jer. 29.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*, zvino wakawanikwa navo\x + 15.4,15. 34.3. 1 Makor. 28.9. Jer. 29.13. Mat. 7.7.\x*, Jehovha ndokuvapa zororo kumativi ese\x + 14.7. 20.30.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Uyewo Maaka mai vaAsa mambo wakamubvisa pauhosi; nokuti waiva aitira chinhu chinonyangadza danda rekunamata naro\x + 1 Madz. 15.13-15.\x*; Asa ndokutemera pasi chinhu chake chinonyangadza, aka\add chi\add*kuyakuya, ndoku\add chi\add*pisa parukova Kidhironi\x + 30.14. 2 Madz. 23.6,15.\x*.
\v 17 Asi nzvimbo dzakakwirira haana kudzibvisa kwaIsraeri; kunyange zvakadaro moyo waAsa waiva wakaperera mazuva ake ese\x + 14.3,5.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Zvino akauisa muimba yaMwari zvinhu zvitsvene zvababa vake nezvinhu zvake zvitsvene, sirivha, negoridhe, nemidziyo.
\v 19 Zvino hakuna kuva nehondo kusvika mugore remakumi matatu nemashanu rekutonga kwaAsa.